'''Guardian of the People''' was the title taken by the leader of the [[Peacekeeper (Outbound Flight Colony)|Peacekeepers]], the law enforcement and security forces of the [[Outbound Flight Colony]]. [[Jorad Pressor]] held the position in [[22 ABY/Legends|22 ABY]].

